    <item>
      <title>中国房主和银行陷入抵押贷款困境</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/china-s-homeowners-and-banks-are-trapped-in-a-mortgage-mess</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在上海，一名金融工作者必须还清逾期的抵押贷款，否则银行将对其提出指控。在杭州，一对夫妇推迟要孩子，并依靠父母帮助偿还房贷；而另一名男子在还款额激增后被迫以 100 万元人民币（13.8 万美元）的损失出售两套房产。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/china-s-homeowners-and-banks-are-trapped-in-a-mortgage-mess</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
